{
  "stem": "10818.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And, and he would come up and every once in a while and visit me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And so that it sort of blossomed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And actually, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he was-- well, he had not been a veteran.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So he didn't get veterans-- the GI Bill to go to college.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he very much wanted to go to college and had been studying music.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we were dating.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And he had his own little business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And my father rather liked that business.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Neither of my parents liked the idea of his going to college and being supported by me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But that's the way it turned out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We-- actually, he went to Texas to study music.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He left rather abruptly at one point, because we weren't going anywhere and getting anywhere.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And so I-- but we stayed in touch.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I went out to Aspen that summer, to the Goethe Bicentennial in 1949.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And he sent me a musical birthday greeting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "He sent me a lullaby that he had written and had it recorded by a friend in Texas.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And then he went to Utah to study.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "He followed a teacher in Utah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And so that was rather touching.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We have it recorded.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I can't sing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It-- it was 'Wynken-- Wynken, Blynken, and Nod.' It was-- he set, he set 'Wynken, Blynken, and Nod' to music.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he, well, there had been another young man who was interested in me when I, I had been in California visiting my cousins.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And some years later, when I went out all that way to Utah, it was suggested that we get in touch.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, where do you want to meet?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course, Frank was in Utah.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
